{"tid":618541,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Messenger訊息證實會被Facebook掃瞄　　像大陸般監控你的相片、連結和內容","createTime":"2018-04-06T01:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T17:27:40.000Z","uid":23677,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"db6f7c7eb588487138abe5766832e48c4e7b0bfe","tid":618541,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"Facebook爆發的私隱問題仍未解決，現在又再爆出多一單新聞。Facebook親口證實，他們會掃描大家在Messenger訊息軟件中的部份內容、連結以至相片，在有需要時會作出干擾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook當然會美化有關事件，稱當年緬甸事件有人在兩派陣營，發放對立的訊息，乘機想製造混亂。當時Messenger就知道有關訊息內容傳播，並阻止緬甸事件濫用其平台。雖然官方稱聊天訊息和內容等是透過機械人掃描，可是Facebook在什麼情況下會插手，又或會人手去閱讀或處理用家的Messenger訊息，則不得而知。<br />\n<br />\n更令人擔心的是，Facebook進入大陸市場後，會否以配合大陸法律制度為名，而監控維權人士或反對政府的Messenger內容，確實值得大家去思考，是否是時候完全停用Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/04/facebook-confirms-scans-your-messenger/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F04%2Ffacebook-confirms-scans-your-messenger%2F&d=BqGjCycW4fN3prVCEleS%2Fv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1a215c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/04/facebook-confirms-scans-your-messenger/</a>"},{"pid":"cc048c10235d9ba5844772e894d2fb6d270603d2","tid":618541,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"693cbfe2a32f18ab10c35c9b6b633f88c58ac60d","tid":618541,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:57:37.000Z","msg":"del得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33026357543966c1ce32728ecade0fd147e0df5e","tid":618541,"uid":230,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"無證據證明whatsapp都會，但同朋友試過講個平時唔講嘅topic,然後好快fb就有廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4991f59